cs.DB, cs.DS, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.SE 

This paper focuses on the design and evaluation of a single-node multidimensional data store for high-velocity sensor data, which involves indexing and retrieval of data. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DB (Databases), followed by cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval). The paper also mentions the use of machine learning techniques for data analysis, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper discusses the implementation and evaluation of a prototype, which is related to cs.SE (Software Engineering).
